      "csl:pageColumn": "1300,3",
      "rdf:value": "<L>263404.1<pc>1300,3<k1>hI<k2>hI<e>1A\r\n¦ (also said to be so used in giving a reason or cause, and translatable by) therefore, so, because, for (<ab>cf.</ab> <hom>2.</hom> <s>hi</s>) &c.<info lex=\"inh\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AhI#record-pwg",
      "@type": "csl:SourceRecord",
