      "csl:recordNumber": "117207",
      "csl:lineNumber": 1095513,
      "csl:pageColumn": "7-1629",
      "rdf:value": "<L>117207<pc>7-1629<k1>hI<k2>hI\n{#hI#}¦ <lex>interj.</lex> {%des Staunens%}\n<ls>AK. 3,5,9.</ls>\n<ls>H. an. 7,17.</ls>\n<ls>MED. avy. 87.</ls> {#hI citram#}\n<ls>BHAṬṬ. 14,39.</ls> {%des Entsetzens%}\n<ls>H. an.</ls> <ls>MED.</ls> {%des Schmerzes%}\n<ls>MED.</ls> verdoppelt {%des Staunens%} und {%Lachens%}\n<ls>H. an. 7,53.</ls>\n<ls>MED. avy. 91.</ls> {%des Behagens%}: {#hI hI (hA hA#} die neuere <ab>Ausg.</ab>) {#hA heti vAdinO#}\n<ls>HARIV. 14578.</ls>\n<LEND>"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AhI#record-pwk",
      "@type": "csl:SourceRecord",
      "dct:source": "Boehtlingk PWK",
      "csl:dictionary": "pwk",
      "csl:recordNumber": "134926",
      "csl:lineNumber": 564071,
      "csl:pageColumn": "7-277-c",
      "rdf:value": "<L>134926<pc>7-277-c<k1>hI<k2>hI\n{#hI#}¦ <ab>Interj.</ab> {%des Staunens, Entsetzens, Scherzes, Lachens%} und {%Behagens%} <ls>Spr. 868</ls> (wo {#hI na#} zu lesen ist; <ab>vgl.</ab> <ls>GAṆAR. S. 7, Z. 10</ls>). <ls>ŚIŚ. 11,64</ls> ({#hI#} <ab>st.</ab> {#hi#} zu lesen, wie schon das Metrum zeigt; <ab>vgl.</ab> auch <ls>GAṆAR. S. 7, Z. 10</ls>). <ls>BĀLAR. 202,4</ls>. <ls>HEM. PAR. 1,350. 409</ls>. <ls>JĀTAKAM. 31,44</ls>. Auch wiederholt <ls>Chr. 300,7</ls>. (im <lang>Prākrit</lang>).\n<LEND>"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3AhI#record-ap90",
      "@type": "csl:SourceRecord",
      "dct:source": "Apte 1890",
      "csl:dictionary": "ap90",
      "csl:recordNumber": "31453",
      "csl:lineNumber": 271596,
      "csl:pageColumn": "1172-c",
      "rdf:value": "<L>31453<pc>1172-c<k1>hI<k2>hI\n{#hI#}¦ {%<ab>ind.</ab>%} An interjection of {@1@} <lbinfo n=\"Sur+prise\"/>\nSurprise (ah!); {#hatIvIDalasitAnAM hI#}\n{#vicitro vipAkaH#} <ls>Śi. 11. 64</ls>; or {#hI#}\n{#citraM lakzmaRenoce#} <ls>Bk. 14. 39</ls>; (often\nrepeated in theatrical language in\nthis sense). {@--2@} Fatigue, <lbinfo n=\"despon+dency\"/>\ndespondency or sorrow. {@--3@} Reason\n(<ab>cf.</ab> {#hi#}). \n<LEND>"
    },
